<h3>About Us</h3>
<p>Kanban for Developers is being developed and maintained by Sand Bridge Software.</p>
<p>Sand Bridge Software is a one-man development shop operated by, Kevin Brinley. Sand Bridge Software was founded in September, 2010. Kanban For Developers, the main product of Sand Bridge Software, began development several months earlier. Sand Bridge Software operates out of Fishers, Indiana.</p>
<p>For more information regarding Sand Bridge Software, please see our <a href="http://blog.kanbanfordevelopers.com/about/">Blog's About page</a></p>
<p>For more information regarding Kanban For Developers, pease see our Blog post, <a href="http://blog.kanbanfordevelopers.com/2010/09/concept-behind-kanban-for-developers/">Concept Behind Kanban For Developers</a></p>
<br />
<p>If you have any questions, comments, or feedback, please contact me at <a href="mailto:kevin@kanbanfordevelopers.com">kevin@kanbanfordevelopers.com</a></p>
